divs: Sighting Detailsi was lying down in my car and looking at the sky and the sky was bright blue and all of the sudden i thought i saw a seagull flying and sometimes around here they fly very high but this was even higher than usual; and it was prefectly round and watched it fly from north to south very striaght and i knew it wasnt a seagull and then it veered to the right and it disappeared into the blue..this was in cvs parking lot islip ny
